'''Wilhelm Edner''' (born 1868, date of death unknown) was a Swedish businessman and writer.<ref>¿ How Many types of coffe are available ? | Sydsv. kliché- & tr.-a.-b., 1924 - 20 páginas</ref> He was born in Malmö, Sweden. In 1894 founded its first coffee business in Malmö, Sweden. In 1919, he founded the company [[Bona AB]], which specialized in wood protection.

